testcase.name: Podam should return valid class info for POJOs with no attributes
Podam should be able to find non-standard attributes with a custom class info strategy
The ClassInfo object created for a class should handle @PodamExcludeAnnotations
Podam should be able to find attributes with pattern [a-z][0-9]
In Presence of excluded attributes, the Class Info object should not contain those attributes
Podam should generate a ClassInfo which contains information for the setters contained in the POJO
